vels\n#oott https://t.co/mCeUVEZVQo", "time": "11:06", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3749, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075537342933217600", "url": "https://x.com/DB_WTI/status/2075537342933217600", "text": "#OOTT #WTI \n#Bombing and a Tentative #Accord Didn’t Work. Does #Trump Have a Plan C for #Iran? https://t.co/0RML4PNIUL", "time": "11:07", "author": "DB_WTI", "author_name": "WTI Trading Group- 🇺🇸 US Crude Oil Trader🛢️🌎", "followers": 12439, "views": 1000, "likes": 1, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075538231928717437", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075538231928717437", "text": "Tanzania’s Richest Man Pledges $100 Million for Dangote Refinery\n#oott https://t.co/k0pg6iurf0", "time": "11:10", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5550, "likes": 5, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075555879122837705", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075555879122837705", "text": "#Russia’s gasoline output covers 65% of demand after Ukrainian strikes, sources say\nMajor refineries halted after Ukrainian drone attacks\nRussia is boosting imports and has banned fuel exports\nOfficials say fuel shortages are a concern\nSupply may increase later in July\n#oott  https://t.co/YKJYY6Cxpr", "time": "12:20", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 11009, "likes": 15, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075560962124341339", "url": "https://x.com/VonburyResearch/status/2075560962124341339", "text": "SPR came down from 325.7M barrels the week before to 319.5M barrels in the EIA report for week ending July 3, 2026.\n\nAnother 6M barrels gone. \nSPR is still being drawn while the Middle East conflict shows no sign of ending.\n\n#OOTT #SPR #Geopolitics https://t.co/WaXyZbqEdx", "time": "12:41", "author": "VonburyResearch", "author_name": "Vonbury Research", "followers": 738, "views": 2461, "likes": 16, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075574882335948996", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2075574882335948996", "text": "Haven't written a long Iran-centric post since all this started 4+ months ago. Guess its time..TLDR version: Iran dynamic will be a wild card for at least another 3 months, anything below $75/bbl WTI is too cheap, watch Hormuz, inventory, China. Read on for the thread! #EFT #OOTT", "time": "13:36", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 19026, "likes": 108, "replies": 16, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 58, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075574945548247523", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2075574945548247523", "text": "On energy lags S&amp;P point, I'll be very happy to be wrong as I'm as bullish about the sector as I've been in several years. But 30%+ of the S&amp;P500 refuses to be wagged by energy's 3%. Good luck out there everyone.I look forward to your observations on my comments above! #EFT #OOTT", "time": "13:36", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 2170, "likes": 19, "replies": 4, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075585080269930659", "url": "https://x.com/SpartaCommo/status/2075585080269930659", "text": "Crude stocks just posted their first build in 11 weeks.\n\nGasoline is drawing down too, but distillates are the real story: down 5 million barrels and now 12% below the 5 year average.\n\nWhy? Abhishek Kumar explains. \n\nWatch the full episode: https://t.co/snYZDwI4P0\n\n#oott #crudeoil #diesel", "time": "14:17", "author": "SpartaCommo", "author_name": "Sparta", "followers": 6127, "views": 783, "likes": 7, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075589265430626654", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2075589265430626654", "text": "Does anyone need a refresher on how to make diesel?\n\nHint: no hopium involved\n\n#oott", "time": "14:33", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 9845, "likes": 45, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 16, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075592584953532478", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2075592584953532478", "text": "In theory, oil inventories shud be negatively correlated to time spreads. Left graph (from my book) confirms it, but recently these correlations became positive !!! (right) with spreads not doing anything despite empty Cushing, highlighting the dominance of other factors. \n#oott https://t.co/3B4Nzi1", "time": "14:46", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 12344, "likes": 91, "replies": 6, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 45, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075623516402266514", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2075623516402266514", "text": "Oil coming out of the Straits of Hormuz probably peaked in the last week or two\n\nNext stop, tank bottoms! #OOTT", "time": "16:49", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 4668, "likes": 30, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075628472529989879", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2075628472529989879", "text": "Baker Hughes Rig Count 07/10\n\n+1 overall, no breakout btw oil and gas available yet @bakerhughesco \n\n#oott #crudeoil #bakerhughes #rigcount", "time": "17:09", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 2460, "likes": 20, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075642119386218934", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2075642119386218934", "text": "We’re hearing tons of noise about the Omani corridor in the SoH, along with this continuous back and forth 'love tap' between DC and Tehran—but looking at the feeds today, hulls are still actively lifting barrels out of the major Middle East hubs.\n\n#oott #iran https://t.co/vHq3heA0Rb", "time": "18:03", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 27444, "likes": 173, "replies": 9, "retweets": 26, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075642502086857153", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2075642502086857153", "text": "Baker Hughes 07/10\nOil +0\nGas +0\nMisc +1\n\n#oott #crudeoil #rigcount", "time": "18:05", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 2019, "likes": 18, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075642789820539115", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075642789820539115", "text": "Money managers reduced their net-length in Brent crude oil futures and options by 547 to 55,087 in the week ending July 7    \n\nLong-only positions fell by 367\nShort-only positions rose by 180\n\nother reportables net-length fell by 34,183\n\nICE #oott", "time": "18:06", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 30382, "likes": 31, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2075727613427921115", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2075727613427921115", "text": "US has cut exports to pre-war levels which may indicate that it has run out of resources to cover global oil deficit.\n\nDespite this it continues to deplete its reserves at rate of 10 mb/wk and may reach bottom of SPR and commercial inventories by August.\n\nheat ahead🔥\n#oott #wti https://t.co/l5hjWu9b", "time": "23:43", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 3898, "likes": 56, "replies": 4, "retweets": 5, "quote